ins with what already exists. We work with reclaimed and surplus textiles, thoughtfully reimagining them into everyday essentials through skilled craftsmanship. You can be a part of this process too - by sharing your own chindis or unused fabric and choosing designs from our collections, we transform them into purposeful pieces made just for you.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","text_align":"left","text_width":"large","additional_text":"","show_view_all":true,"button_label":"Get Started","button_style":"primary","button_link":"","margin_top":"s","margin_bottom":"no-indent"}},"multicolumn_hwctAB":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_6KwnJk":{"type":"column","settings":{"icon":"return","heading":"Give your left over fabric","text":"<p>We begin with textile remnants -offcuts, surplus fabric, and unused cloth -collected and carefully sorted by material, colour, and quality.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","show_button":false,"button_label":"Discover More","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","full_link":false,"additional_text_1":"","additional_text_2":""}},"column_rCckJK":{"type":"column","settings":{"icon":"question_mark_1","heading":"Choose a design","text":"<p>Select from Sattva's collections or work with us to adapt an existing design. Each piece is thoughtfully planned to make the most of the material at hand.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","show_button":false,"button_label":"Discover More","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","full_link":false,"additional_text_1":"","additional_text_2":""}},"column_4MTHPi":{"type":"column","settings":{"icon":"moon","heading":"We make it","text":"<p>Skilled women artisans bring the design to life through careful stitching, finishing, and quality checks turning what once remained unused into something purposeful.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","show_button":false,"button_label":"Discover More","button_link":"","button_style":"primary","full_link":false,"additional_text_1":"","additional_text_2":""}}},"block_order":["column_6KwnJk","column_rCckJK","column_4MTHPi"],"disabled